		</ul>		
		<strong><p class="text-info">IFace's Certificate Authentication Solution will help in the validation of certificates and documents issued by organizations and institution for its authenticity through the use of technologies stated in the following pragraphs.
The proposed Solution will give more reliability robustness, security and foolproof functionality, which are not available in the country’s present system of issuance of SSLC, 12th certificates, and mark sheets to school students.</p></strong>
		<p class="lead">Major Problems</p>
<p>
1. Custom Made Fake Mark Sheets, Diplomas, Fake College Degrees and Transcripts Available in the market<br/>
2. Cost Ranging from Rs 10,000 – Rs 50,000<br/>
3. At least a dozens of websites offering Professional FAKE Certificates<br/>
4. Replicated, Fake Class X/XII, Degrees/Diplomas from most post-secondary institutions from around the world are &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Available(Fake Certificate Making companies have over 3000 templates on file) all designed to look 100% identical to &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the original<br/>
5. Class X/XII, Higher Secondary, Matriculation, GCSE, A-levels, Diploma Certificates and University certificates<br/>
6. GMAT, MCAT, and LSAT Examination Certificates<br/>
7. A survey says: India is the biggest manufacturer of fake degrees in the World!<br/>
8. It is impossible to get each certificate verified as resources are limited<br/>
9. Class X Certificates are used everywhere for identification starting from bank account opening, Issuing of Ration card, &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Driving license to passport verification Immigration Frauds, ID Theft, Fake documents to get Government Benefits<br/>
10. As Per the International and Indian law personal details of any citizens should not be published online without his/her &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;permission. So Government cannot maintain an open system for verification process through online</p>
